    "15734900": {
      "title": "Evaluating the impact of the alcohol act on off-trade alcohol sales: a natural experiment in Scotland",
      "abstract": "Background and Aims ::: A ban on multi-buy discounts of off-trade alcohol was introduced as part of the Alcohol Act in Scotland in October 2011. The aim of this study was to assess the impact of this legislation on alcohol sales, which provide the best indicator of population consumption."
